{"tid":1837010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"良心黃店而又有口罩賣嘅過入黎睇","createTime":"2020-01-23T12:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T12:53:02.000Z","uid":289442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cb78cd26030950e7bd1cf2594d0d43946860db35","tid":1837010,"uid":289442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:13:55.000Z","msg":"依家周街都搶緊口罩，一係就炒價<br />\n你哋點解仲要益班藍絲廢老可以平入口罩，搞到真手足要捱貴嘢？咁仲係咪黃色經濟圈嘅理念呀？<br />\n<br />\n我建議黃店良心店賣良心價嘅同時要嗌口號/要附帶捐款<br />\n至少幫到其他手足又可以杜絕啲仆街廢老藍絲黎拎著數<br />\n有咩提議都可以改吓，同意嘅幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6209fe3e460fdcbdebe0d501bca74f01b040cdf1","tid":1837010,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:16:38.000Z","msg":"貼連儂牆先可以買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d4f7470f04be9ba3a0ef35fbe893dd7c6a89a9","tid":1837010,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:21:52.000Z","msg":"咁做可以淺籃轉黃lo"},{"pid":"f6abcd7196c4b669ce8e664d77e2c6b14eca2a17","tid":1837010,"uid":289442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57d4f7470f04be9ba3a0ef35fbe893dd7c6a89a9","tid":1837010,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:21:52.000Z","msg":"咁做可以淺籃轉黃lo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T12:53:02.000Z","msg":"益佢哋唔會轉黃架<br />\n排得慢仲會屌鳩你<br />\n佢哋自私到一個地步"}]}